WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.350
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:05.670
Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:08.950
Well, it's Diana, my beautiful bride,

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.669
and me. We're excited to be

00:00:11.679 --> 00:00:13.990
here today. I try to embarrass her as

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:15.190
much as I can when she's

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.910
sitting next to me. You

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:19.510
don't know how many times we do these

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:22.230
takes, and I try to be funny. I told

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.070
her, "It's making her

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:29.189
laugh."If

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:30.870
you can't have fun doing what you're

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:33.030
doing, then why do it, right?

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:35.350
It's exciting times. This is what Jesus is

00:00:35.360 --> 00:00:37.430
talking to us about. Nothing is going to

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:39.350
happen in the natural unless we

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:41.670
pray it through in the spiritual first.

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:44.549
We must intercede and pray for what's

00:00:44.559 --> 00:00:45.670
coming.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:47.830
He talked about it even today. I was

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:49.350
driving around, and Diana had to go into the

00:00:49.360 --> 00:00:51.670
grocery store.

00:00:51.680 --> 00:00:54.310
The Lord started talking about cars,

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.790
people driving around in their cars, and

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:59.029
the cars looking like they were on fire when the glory

00:00:59.029 --> 00:00:59.039
was

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:00.869
on them. He said, "Brandon, I'm

00:01:00.879 --> 00:01:02.389
going to do something very

00:01:02.389 --> 00:01:02.399
unusual."And

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:04.310
I said, "Lord, what is that?"He said,

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.870
"The fire was on buildings last time

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:08.710
whenever Azusa Street happened.

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:10.710
People saw fire on the

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:13.510
buildings when Rodney Howard-Browne held

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.990
meetings in Fort Worth, Texas. The

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.670
building looked like it was on fire,

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.749
and the fire department came, but the

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:21.830
building was not on fire. It was on fire

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:23.670
with the Holy Ghost, and they were seeing

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.109
in the spirit realm a building that was

00:01:25.119 --> 00:01:27.350
on fire."The Lord told me,

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.670
"Brandon, what I'm about to do is that

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:32.710
when people are driving around on

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:34.390
the streets, it's going to look like

00:01:34.400 --> 00:01:37.270
their car is on fire. I'm going to show up

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:39.350
in their car as they're interceding,

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:41.590
driving around the city,

00:01:41.600 --> 00:01:43.190
and your car is going to look like

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.630
you're on fire. People are going to

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:48.149
be staring, thinking your car is on fire,

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.990
as a sign and a wonder in these last

00:01:49.990 --> 00:01:50.000
days—not

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:53.350
just on buildings, but on you

00:01:53.360 --> 00:01:55.270
when you walk in like Shadrach, Meshach,

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:57.749
and Abednego. You're in

00:01:57.759 --> 00:02:00.550
a Holy Ghost fire. They were in an actual

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:04.230
fire. But I'm talking about a real fire

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:06.550
that they see on us. They

00:02:06.550 --> 00:02:06.560
will

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.550
go, 'What is going on with that

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:12.390
guy? He's on fire.'It's the glory. It's

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:14.790
the glory."Ladies and gentlemen, it's

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:17.750
time to anticipate the demonstrations

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:19.990
and manifestations of the glory of

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.910
God.

00:02:21.920 --> 00:02:24.869
Over the past 30 or 40 years, or whatever

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:26.390
you've had in your life, the Lord has

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:27.910
shown me, He said, "Brandon, it's been a

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:30.550
cultivation with folks. Not everybody is

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:32.309
going to walk in the greater

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:34.229
supernatural miracles because

00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:35.670
they're not there yet. They'll

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:38.150
try to take the glory for it. Do you

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:41.910
understand? God will use you in an

00:02:41.920 --> 00:02:44.470
unusual way if you know how to deflect

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:47.750
the glory to

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:47.760
Him."The

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:50.390
Lord told me, "If

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:53.589
you don't take the glory, Brandon, I'll

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:55.750
use you to do great and mighty things.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:59.350
As long as you always deflect it like a

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.030
mirror, deflecting the glory to

00:03:01.040 --> 00:03:04.790
Him. You attract to deflect. As long as

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:06.869
you deflect the glory in these last

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:09.430
days, I'll use you mightily.""But

00:03:09.430 --> 00:03:09.440
there are

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:12.630
many people who will not deflect

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:14.229
it. They'll try to take it.

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:16.790
And He said, 'I will not share my glory

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:19.670
with any

00:03:19.670 --> 00:03:19.680
man.'For

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:21.509
what I'm about to do in these last

00:03:21.519 --> 00:03:23.830
days, no one has ever seen what's

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:26.149
about to happen. No eye has seen, no ear

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:28.309
has heard, nor has it entered into the heart of

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.949
man the things that God has prepared for

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:33.830
those that love Him. Listen, ladies and

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:35.990
gentlemen, God is about to show up and

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:37.750
show off in your life in an

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:40.789
unprecedented way

00:03:40.789 --> 00:03:40.799
that's

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.430
going to be shock and awe.

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:46.070
But He will not share His glory with

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.070
what's about to take place. And if He

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:51.190
can trust you to deflect it as a

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:54.229
general, then He'll use you

00:03:54.229 --> 00:03:54.239
mightily."He

00:03:54.239 --> 00:03:56.309
showed me it's going

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:57.990
to be like a change in command in the

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:00.070
natural, like we have in the army.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.830
We have the generals, then it

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:03.670
goes to lieutenant generals, and it keeps

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:06.149
going down, right? The Lord showed

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:08.070
me

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.910
that it is just like that in the spirit

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.070
realm. And the ones that pay the price

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:14.630
and are willing to say,

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:17.430
"I deflect. Father, it's not

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:19.590
me. It's You."I just want everybody to

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.270
know immediately when you're in a crowd

00:04:21.270 --> 00:04:21.280
and

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:22.710
you're on fire with the glory,

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:24.790
it's all about Jesus. This isn't about

00:04:24.800 --> 00:04:27.430
attracting attention to me. This isn't

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:28.950
about how great I am. It's about how

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:31.270
great He is. He's able to operate

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:32.790
through this vessel. Ladies and gentlemen, I have this

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:35.110
treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power may be of Him and not of me. This is important. With what we're about to see—when we see the legs, the arms, the ears, and the dead being raised—we must remember we have this treasure

00:04:35.110 --> 00:04:35.120
in

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:36.710
earthen

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:38.629
vessels, that the

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:40.469
excellency of the power will be known of

00:04:40.479 --> 00:04:43.590
Him and not of me.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:04.070
I decrease, He

00:05:04.070 --> 00:05:04.080
increases.

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:06.790
As long as we have a heart

00:05:06.790 --> 00:05:06.800
where

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:09.110
He is increasing and we are

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:11.510
decreasing, we are deflecting and looking

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:14.950
at Him. He is the potter, I am the clay.

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:16.870
He is not sharing His

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:18.550
glory with anyone. He could use

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:21.430
anybody, but He's not

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.350
sharing the glory. It's

00:05:23.360 --> 00:05:26.070
all about Him and nothing about me. I'm

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:27.909
just a vessel that He uses in these end

00:05:27.919 --> 00:05:30.550
times. Do you understand? We

00:05:30.550 --> 00:05:30.560
attract

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:32.070
to deflect,

00:05:32.080 --> 00:05:33.909
and it's very important. The Lord

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:36.710
showed me today that as we are getting

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:38.950
ready to see demonstrations and

00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.790
manifestations like we've never seen

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:43.029
before, He said, "If you want to be a

00:05:43.039 --> 00:05:46.070
general in my army, know that I will

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:47.990
not share my glory with anybody."People

00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:48.000
will say,

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:50.469
"Well, look at him.

00:05:50.479 --> 00:05:52.390
He's on fire. Can you believe that?

00:05:52.400 --> 00:05:54.310
Did you know that Sister Diana has

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:57.270
raised 30 people from the dead?

00:05:57.280 --> 00:06:00.390
Boy, she's something, isn't

00:06:00.390 --> 00:06:00.400
she?"She's

00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:02.230
a child of the King, and I'm a child

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:03.909
of the King. We're all just doing

00:06:03.919 --> 00:06:06.710
exactly what He's called us to do, and He

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.950
can use anybody.

00:06:08.950 --> 00:06:08.960
Keep

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:11.350
your eyes on Him and stay focused.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:13.189
It's important that you do this. You

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:15.029
need to hear me because of what He's

00:06:15.039 --> 00:06:17.909
told me is coming.

00:06:17.919 --> 00:06:21.189
Unusual signs and wonders beyond

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:23.590
anybody's comprehension are about to take

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:26.230
place in the body of Christ. Unusual

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:31.270
demonstrations, unusual miracles,

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:34.309
things we've never seen before.

00:06:34.319 --> 00:06:37.510
If God showed up with the

00:06:37.520 --> 00:06:39.350
glory on Moses's face, He said,

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:40.870
"Brandon, I'm going to show up

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:40.880
with

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:45.110
even greater glory on you. Watch if you

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:47.590
learn to

00:06:47.590 --> 00:06:47.600
deflect."Keep

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:49.990
learning. Keep dying to self.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.670
That's why the Apostle Paul said, "I die

00:06:51.670 --> 00:06:51.680
daily."I

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:55.189
will not take the glory. When

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:57.590
the shadow of Peter walked down

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:59.350
through wherever the people

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.589
were sick, the glory touched

00:07:01.589 --> 00:07:01.599
them.

00:07:01.599 --> 00:07:02.950
He didn't even have to lay hands on

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:04.469
them; the glory of the Lord touched

00:07:04.479 --> 00:07:06.629
these people, right?

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:07.670
The shadow touched

00:07:07.670 --> 00:07:07.680
them.

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:09.510
When the shadow touched them, it was the

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:09.990
glory.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.749
It wasn't him; it was just a

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:12.150
shadow.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.749
The glory was radiating out of him so

00:07:15.749 --> 00:07:15.759
strongly

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:19.909
and so

00:07:19.909 --> 00:07:19.919
powerfully

00:07:19.919 --> 00:07:23.350
that even the shadow touched

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.870
them.

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:26.469
That's what the Lord showed me during my prayer time

00:07:26.479 --> 00:07:27.830
all day today, just driving around.

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:30.870
He said, "Brandon, you must

00:07:30.880 --> 00:07:33.909
keep this in mind all the time. You have

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:36.390
a treasure in an earthen vessel, that the

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:38.230
excellency of the power will be known of

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:41.110
Him and not of you."This treasure that

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:43.510
you carry—He said, "You don't share

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:45.909
your treasure until I tell you

00:07:45.919 --> 00:07:51.029
to share it. It's not your gift. It's my

00:07:51.039 --> 00:07:54.309
gift being distributed through you. The

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:57.350
gold and the silver are mine.

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:59.830
The cattle are mine. The anointing and

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:03.350
the glory

00:08:03.350 --> 00:08:03.360
are

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.629
mine."This

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:07.189
endless treasure that you carry in earthen vessels is a treasure.

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:12.469
The power of the Holy

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:15.029
Spirit is a treasure in an

00:08:15.029 --> 00:08:15.039
earthen

00:08:15.039 --> 00:08:18.150
vessel. And He showed me a vast supply.

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:20.230
And He said, "The supply will never run

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:23.350
dry, Brandon. It will never run dry

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.110
with anything that I've called you to

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:29.830
do. There is a vast supply."Come to the

00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:31.670
river.

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.589
Hallelujah.

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:37.029
I feel the Holy Spirit right now.

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:39.029
He showed me this treasure and all

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:41.589
these coins, and He said, "Just because

00:08:41.599 --> 00:08:43.589
you have it and you operate in it,

00:08:43.599 --> 00:08:45.990
Brandon, doesn't mean it's for you to

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.630
just do what you want to do with

00:08:48.630 --> 00:08:48.640
it."You

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:50.949
are a steward of what I've called you to

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:54.790
do. Listen, you are a steward of the

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:56.630
money, of the wealth, of the glory.

00:08:56.640 --> 00:08:58.070
That's what I want to say. The vast

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:59.829
supply, the treasure in

00:08:59.829 --> 00:08:59.839
earthen

00:08:59.839 --> 00:09:01.910
vessels.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:04.070
You have that treasure inside of you,

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:06.070
ladies and gentlemen, and you're a

00:09:06.080 --> 00:09:08.070
steward of it.

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:09.829
'What do you want me to do

00:09:09.839 --> 00:09:12.389
with this, Lord?'And He said, 'You don't

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:14.470
let everybody touch the treasure, and you

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:16.790
don't tell everybody about

00:09:16.790 --> 00:09:16.800
it.'Because

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:19.590
it's precious.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.590
The way you guard it and you

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.870
protect it. And as you distribute it,

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:27.190
you distribute the coins

00:09:27.190 --> 00:09:27.200
out—the

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:28.470
treasure in

00:09:28.470 --> 00:09:28.480
earthen vessels—you

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.310
distribute those out to the people that

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.790
He tells you to.

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.389
This is exactly what I've asked you to

00:09:34.399 --> 00:09:36.630
do today.

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:38.870
Jesus said, 'I do nothing unless my

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:41.910
Father instructs me to do

00:09:41.910 --> 00:09:41.920
it.'Even

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.430
if He thought, 'Well, I'm the Son

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:45.509
of God. Are you kidding me? I can do

00:09:45.519 --> 00:09:47.110
whatever I want to do. Are you kidding

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:50.870
me? I'm Jesus.'No, He went about it

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:53.670
even more humbled and dead to self. 'I do

00:09:53.680 --> 00:09:56.230
nothing unless I hear my Father tell me

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:59.750
to do it,'regardless of what He thought

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:02.870
or what He could have done. 'I only do

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:06.150
what I'm instructed to by my

00:10:06.150 --> 00:10:06.160
Father.'And

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.310
that's exactly how He operated the

00:10:08.320 --> 00:10:09.750
whole time He was walking underneath the

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:10.949
glory,

00:10:10.959 --> 00:10:13.990
and that's what we should do. We

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.069
have this treasure in earthen vessels, and it's

00:10:16.079 --> 00:10:17.990
coins. It's beautiful gold. It's

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:20.069
beautiful diamonds. What do you do with

00:10:20.079 --> 00:10:21.670
that in distributing it out to the

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:24.069
people? Only do what the Father tells

00:10:24.079 --> 00:10:27.430
you to do. I have a treasure, and in

00:10:27.430 --> 00:10:27.440
these

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:30.550
scriptures that He gives me today,

00:10:30.560 --> 00:10:32.150
the excellency of the power will be

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:35.190
known to Him. I attract to deflect, and I

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:37.509
always make sure I'm never going to

00:10:37.519 --> 00:10:40.310
share the glory with the Lord. It's all

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:42.150
about Him and nothing about me. Does

00:10:42.160 --> 00:10:44.870
that make sense? You have to keep this

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:46.870
in your heart. He said, 'Those that do

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:50.389
this, I will use even greater.

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:52.470
They'll be ranked in the military in the

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:54.550
spiritual realm.'Who will be used?

00:10:54.560 --> 00:10:55.990
He said, 'There's a lot of them I will

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:58.069
not be able to trust because the moment

00:10:58.079 --> 00:11:00.389
